name: Superkitties
overview: An adorable and action-packed new series about four fierce and furry superhero kittens — Ginny, Sparks, Buddy and Bitsy — who are on a mission to make Kittydale a more caring and ”pawesome” place.

episodes.name: The Great Yarn Caper
episodes.overview: The SuperKitties must figure out why someone is stealing all the yarn in Kittydale.

episodes.name: Get the Boot
episodes.overview: Lab Rat invents a giant boot to smush all the flowers at the Kittydale Flower Festival.

episodes.name: Fireworks Fright
episodes.overview: Mr. Puppypaws steals all of Kittydale’s fireworks.

episodes.name: Cheese Trees
episodes.overview: The SuperKitties have to stop Lab Rat from turning Kittydale into cheese.

episodes.name: Silent Surprise

episodes.name: Fufu Snafu

episodes.name: Super-Fan
episodes.overview: SuperKitty super-fan, Pickles, helps the team save the day.

episodes.name: Bubble Bother

episodes.name: Missing Mr. Greenie

episodes.name: Piano Problem
episodes.overview: When the abandoned piano Cat Burglar is playing suddenly gets damaged, he takes one from two musicians who are about to perform on stage.

episodes.name: Treat Truck Trouble
episodes.overview: All the pet food in Kittydale is replaced with dog food.

episodes.name: Leapin' Laser

episodes.overview: When Mr. Puppypaws' fetching stick is snubbed by other dogs who see another one, he attempts to make a better stick with wood from the park.

episodes.name: Rockin' Rockhound
episodes.overview: The Superkitties are summoned to protect a new artifact at the museum.
